Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:06.81,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是晚上了 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:06.81,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,もう夜だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.71,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么把窗帘拉开?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.71,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしてカーテンなんか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.44,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你看 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.44,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,だって
